Orbit Onboarding is a centralized onboarding and knowledge management platform built using Spring Boot, Spring Security, JWT authentication, PostgreSQL, and Spring Data JPA. The application allows users to register, access training modules, read knowledge articles, and track onboarding progress. I implemented layered architecture with controllers for handling requests, services for business logic, repositories for database interaction, and entities mapped using JPA. Security is handled through JWT-based stateless authentication with BCrypt password encryption. Module progress tracking uses relational mapping and database constraints to ensure users complete modules only once. Swagger was integrated for API testing and documentation.
